research_municipality_step.notes: The elected officials for Ovilla, TX, include the Mayor and five Council Members. Kimberly Case also holds the role of Mayor Pro Tem. All council positions are elected at-large. Information was gathered from the official City of Ovilla website and the TML City Officials Directory.
